SOTD is Terre D'Hermès Parfum

This is my favorite flanker in the line. It still has the base DNA but with some more spice and woodsy notes. The oak moss is definitely appreciated in here and the benzoin comes off a little resinous. I absolutely love this one. 

Top notes are Orange and Grapefruit; middle note is Flint; base notes are Woodsy Notes, oak moss and Benzoin.

Rakuten fashion week Tokyo ss24 is in full swing, running from Monday, August 28 to Saturday, September 2, 2023. As is always the case, attendees take their attire very seriously.
